## ğŸ›  Components Prepared

### Buttons (`btn/primary`)
- States: `default`, `hover`, `pressed`, `disabled`
- Auto Layout, Padding: 12px / 8px
- Radius: 8px, Font: Roboto 20px, Text: Black

### Inputs
- States: `default`, `focused`, `error`
- Placeholder style, consistent border-radius

### Tags / Badges
- Variants: `tag/primary`, `tag/alt`
- Rounded: 16px radius

### Cards
- Job Card with hover shadow
- Consistent padding and spacing
- Variants documented

### Modal / Popups
- Structured with header, body, CTA
- Optional close icon, overlay.

## ğŸ¨ Design Tokens

### Typography (Font: Roboto)
| Token | Size | Weight | Use Case |
|-------|------|--------|----------|
| `text/h1` | 48px | Bold | Hero Headings |
| `text/h2` | 36px | SemiBold | Section Headers |
| `text/h3` | 32px | Medium | Card Titles |
| `text/body` | 25px | Regular | Descriptions |
| `text/caption` | 20px | Light | Meta Info |
| `text/Caption` | 12px | Light | Skills Require |

### Colors
- `color/primary`: `#0F0072, #FFB026, #E66800, #DCD6FF`
- `color/secondary`: `#0055CD`
- `color/text/dark`: `#000000`
- `color/text/light`: `#FFFFFF`
- `color/gradient`: `linear(90Â°, #0083C5, #A8DDE5, #AFACC2, #4536A2, #CAE0FF, #0057D6)`

### Spacing (4px scale)
- `spacing/4` â†’ 4px
- `spacing/8` â†’ 8px
- `spacing/16` â†’ 16px
- `spacing/24` â†’ 24px
- `spacing/32` â†’ 32px


